}}2016年3月26日，加拿大飞机维护公司特克尼克航空（Aero Teknic）的一架[[三菱MU-2|三菱MU-2]]在{{le|伊莱斯·德·拉·玛德琳机场|Îles-de-la-Madeleine Airport}}降落时坠毁。机上无人生还。前加拿大政治家{{le|让·拉皮埃尔|Jean Lapierre}}遇难。他本是和他的妻子，姐姐和两个兄弟去搭乘这架飞机参加父亲的葬礼的。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://ici.radio-canada.ca/nouvelles/societe/2016/03/30/003-pascal-gosselin-pilote-avion-iles-madeleine-ecrasement-pionnier-internet-quebec.shtml|title=Îles-de-la-Madeleine: le pilote Pascal Gosselin était un pionnier d'Internet au Québec|date=30 March 2016|work=[[CBC.ca|Ici Radio-Canada.ca]]|accessdate=31 March 2016|last1=Grou|first1=Vincent|archive-date=2016-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160912172545/http://ici.radio-canada.ca/nouvelles/societe/2016/03/30/003-pascal-gosselin-pilote-avion-iles-madeleine-ecrasement-pionnier-internet-quebec.shtml}}</ref> 救援人员赶到现场时，发现了一名受重伤的幸存者，但把他从残骸中救出来之后，这名男子就因心脏病发作而死。<ref name="CTVM">{{Cite news|url=http://montreal.ctvnews.ca/seven-dead-in-iles-de-la-madeleine-plane-crash-sq-1.2836733|title=Seven dead in Iles de la Madeleine plane crash: SQ|work=[[CTV_Montreal|CTV Montreal]]|accessdate=29 March 2016}}</ref><ref name="CBC">{{Cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/magdalen-islands-plane-crash-1.3510975|title=Breaking Îles-de-la-Madeleine leaves 6 dead, 1 man injured|date=29 March 2016|work=[[CBC_News|CBC News]]|accessdate=29 March 2016|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129053358/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/magdalen-islands-plane-crash-1.3510975}}</ref><ref name="Authier">{{Cite news|url=http://montrealgazette.com/news/local-news/plane-believed-to-be-carrying-jean-lapierre-and-his-family-crashes-on-iles-de-la-madeleine|title=Seven people dead following plane crash on Îles-de-la-Madeleine, SQ says|date=29 March 2016|work=[[Montreal_Gazette|Montreal Gazette]]|accessdate=29 March 2016|last1=Authier|first1=Philip|archive-date=2021-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210525055721/https://montrealgazette.com/news/local-news/plane-believed-t