== 事故 ==
东部时间9:30，这架飞机离开{{le|蒙特利尔隆格伊·圣休伯特机场|Montreal Saint-Hubert Longueuil Airport}}。大约70分钟后（大西洋时间11:40），飞机在目的地机场2公里外的地方坠毁。<ref name="CBC2">{{Cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/jean-lapierre-dead-plane-crash-%C3%AEles-de-la-madeleine-1.3510975|title=Jean Lapierre among 7 killed in Îles-de-la-Madeleine plane crash|date=29 March 2016|publisher=CBC News|accessdate=29 March 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108134913/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/jean-lapierre-dead-plane-crash-%C3%AEles-de-la-madeleine-1.3510975}}</ref><ref name="TSB1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.tsb.gc.ca/eng/enquetes-investigations/aviation/2016/a16a0032/a16a0032.asp|title=Aviation Investigation A16A0032|accessdate=29 March 2016|date=29 March 2016|publisher=Transportation Safety Board of Canada|archive-date=2018-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180116205743/http://www.tsb.gc.ca/eng/enquetes-investigations/aviation/2016/a16a0032/a16a0032.asp}}</ref>

